sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' function RowDetails({customerName, customerAdress, customerMobileNumber, Id, OnDelete, countryCode, countryName, operatorName}) { return ( {customerName} {customerAdress} {customerMobileNumber} {countryCode} {countryName} {operatorName} OnDelete(Id)}> ) } export default RowDetails
